Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇~ 鯛魚燒麵包~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:41.62,Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fs42\fad(450,400)\blur6\pos(1002,160)}王子的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯~  就是這一味~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不吃這個的話一天就無法開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯~ 真好吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然作為店員說這話有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你每天吃都吃不膩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}偶爾換換其他麵包怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貓型麵包也有哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喵！~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咿呀！！！~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從那之後王國的人有說過什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有異議的話去城堡裡說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們只負責回收從海裡打撈上來的東西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這算什麼嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼非得要全部都被王國拿走啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全沒消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擱淺的船也是小梅還回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}稍微給點獎勵也沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吶...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯...　算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？ 難道不會很不甘心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒這種事的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的！ 虧大本了啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妮莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下一批麵包烤好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去幫忙拿出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 歡迎下次再來~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多謝惠顧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯~ 做的不錯~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是酸莓泡芙蛋糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}酸酸甜甜的 好香呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輝夜今天醒著就好了呢~  里克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天是你來送麵包的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輝夜的身體狀況如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯... 今天早上還在睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肚子餓了醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吃了你們的麵包後又馬上睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吃過麵包的話就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阿哩嘎豆~ 大姊姊~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來~ 吃吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好香的味道啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾雅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輝夜的情況怎麼樣了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天沒見到面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還在睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊... 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}漏雨的地方已經修好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有其他損壞的地方也完全修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然知道這是很唐突的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃... 可不可以幫忙一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是這裡的麵包師吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像是城堡裡的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是露菲娜王女的侍女 蘿娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被拉格納斯王子和露菲娜大人吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前來訂製麵包了呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感謝你 特地過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是他們訂的是鬆餅和田園麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:37.69,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\blur5\bord1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(835,652)}campagne
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:37.69,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur1}Campagne : 源自法語，田園麵包。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說想吃沙丁魚和番茄的普切塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.90,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&\pos(832,656)}Bruschetta
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.90,NOTE,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur1}Bruschetta：意大利的一種前菜。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鬆餅倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天沒做田園麵包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.95,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\blur5\bord1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(704,659)}campagne
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是非常不好意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我想趁天還亮著的時候送去城堡裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:06:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的... 王國的人都不會替周圍的人著想 真是為所欲為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管什麼時候都不體諒一下 我們的工作時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妮莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}王子和公主是不是真的這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}送麵包的時候親自確認一下 不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是現在開始做的話 還來得及嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可以幫忙製作！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是溫達利亞城的廚師群的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很瞭解拉格納斯王子喜歡的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}餡料的話 由我來進行準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.41,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\blur5\bord1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(743,654)}campagne
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼就由我們做田園麵包吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘿~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好熟練的手法呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧為王國的廚師呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}深藏不露呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下來等到城堡之後再用西洋醋和羅勒腌泡一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為要送到城堡裡 有什麼能裝的容器...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是冒失娘啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}冒失娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是冒失娘呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:44.90,Title2,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\fad(450,400)\blur4\pos(640,623)}— 溫達利亞城 —
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仔細看看 還真是好大的城堡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺這個地方很難接近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們幾個在那邊想搞什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎... 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們是過來送麵包的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麵包！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真可疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們是拉格納斯大人和露菲娜大人的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我剛才又摔倒...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蘿娜沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛... 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們繼續出發吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的啊！ 什麼叫可疑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們可是被邀請過來的呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘻~ 不要臉~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好厲害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全都是薔薇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好漂亮~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎來到我的薔薇花園
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}露菲娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是魯克魯的各位 接受訂單外送麵包過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是辛苦你們特地前來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以的話一起喝杯紅茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比那盛開的薔薇更美麗的少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}獻上這首曲子給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}(抽吸)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太精彩了 拉格納斯大人~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看起來好美味的普切塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.54,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&\pos(776,657)}Bruschetta
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和露菲娜的紅茶真是絕配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝 多虧了蘿娜的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蘿娜的廚藝確實不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝贊...贊...贊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我認為用你們的麵包所做成的普切塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.47,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&\pos(894,656)}Bruschetta
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嚐起來一定會很美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能和我們聊一下城堡外的狀況嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}外面的事情 我們沒什麼機會能接觸到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有關最近暴風雨的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有個女孩漂流到海岸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}漂流者 和你的情況一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起露菲娜 我對外面的事情瞭解的多一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們好像之前從海裡撈出一個巨大的箱子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那...那個 關於那個箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們剛撈上岸 就被城裡的士兵給沒收了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要那麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是因為這座島上的規定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在溫達利亞裡 海中所找到的埋藏物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必需暫時由王國來進行管理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是... 明明是我們好不容易找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那些是不是危險的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是不是正當的所有者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為王室的責任 必須好好的檢查一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊... 原來是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然 找到這些東西人會得到獎賞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是調查還需要點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛... 反正最後結果都一樣 無所謂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果找的東西很值錢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會不會像上次整修教會一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}整修教會？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們並不知道這件事...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打擾了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}城內的定期巡視 沒有發現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告辭！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總覺得 城裡的警備好像特別森嚴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯... 其實最近城堡裡有小偷出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小偷只有一人 自稱怪盜黑尾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:27.05,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\bord1\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&\pos(842,656)}Black tail
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}順便能請你們幫忙抓小偷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一位作為漂流者的劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很早以前就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哥哥 大家都很為難的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 哥哥經常開這種玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為單單靠那些衛兵是防不住的 這也是沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會讓你們單獨上陣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會派蘿娜為你們帶路的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了抓住小偷 你幫里克他們帶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}交.... 交付我如此艱巨的任務 真是太感...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然 做的不錯的話 也會進行賞賜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}獎...獎勵？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓里克去抓小偷這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說的也是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然很感謝你這麼看重我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是挺好的嗎 里克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我們也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以作為爐子的修理費的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 你們能接受呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是不好意思呢 不過太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}並且 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這件工作 再算上我一份 可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘿~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是厲害的劍術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然很久沒看到你這身打扮了 很適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我自己倒是記不太清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倒是妮莉絲竟然會用弓箭 真是讓我大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別看我這樣 我可是很有本事的哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 我們去城堡裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這前面就是連接城堡的上下螺旋階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有地下啊 城堡果然很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是沒有蘿娜的話 可能一不小心就迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不！ 我總是很冒失的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天都會摔一次並且暈過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一次...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總是給拉格納斯大人和露菲娜大人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算這樣 他們還是選擇把你留在身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得 這一定是因為你有屬於自己的魅力之處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣的嗎~ 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下來是往東邊巡視...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行給我看！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有把他那時候穿的衣服還給他了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊~ 把東西全部還給他還太早了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有小偷！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在哪裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小偷在哪啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黑尾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.02,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\bord1\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&\pos(640,654)}black tail
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑哪去了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黑尾！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.73,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\bord1\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&\pos(622,652)}black tail
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小偷 逃到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蘿娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身為一位溫達利亞的廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收拾這種壞人也是我們的工作！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 我們追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我站住 黑尾！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.04,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\bord1\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&\pos(707,652)}black tail
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個前面是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到書庫就是死路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在哪...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黑尾！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.65,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\bord1\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&\pos(625,648)}black tail
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乖乖的束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分頭追吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克 蘿娜 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蘿娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然動不了 但是沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不准給我動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}里克 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓他逃了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太遺憾了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拉格納斯大人 露菲娜大人 真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒逮到黑尾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.00,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\bord1\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&\pos(700,656)}black tail
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們已經做的很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多虧了你們這次才沒有東西被偷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然書庫變得亂七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊~ 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}書只要重新放好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們成功擊退了小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請收下獎勵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以看一眼嗎！~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 別這樣啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只看一眼的話~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蘿娜有幫上忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然 多虧了蘿娜才能把小偷逼到那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 真是做的不錯
